{"tid":1024313,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"貴過iphone！LG G8 未出 V50 就到？","createTime":"2019-02-16T12:42:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-06T21:21:24.000Z","uid":22675,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":33,"replies":[{"pid":"f5c52f8d4a2ee67b3aba7715bd0d126b4dcad296","tid":1024313,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-16T12:42:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://m.ringhk.com/editor/news2018/20190216_lgv50_01.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.ringhk.com%2Feditor%2Fnews2018%2F20190216_lgv50_01.jpg&h=43c7f940&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n <br />\n唔少 Android 廠商都有雙旗艦的策略，分別用兩款旗艦手機支撐起上、下半年的銷量，除了 Samsung 的 S / Note、華為的 P / Mate 之外，LG 也有 G / V 兩大系列，當中 G8 ThinQ 預計在月底的 MWC2019 上正式登場。<br />\n<br />\n不過尷尬的是，LG 為搶佔 5G 先機，除了旗艦機 G8 之外，也預計將於 MWC2019 上發表跟美國網絡商 Sprint 合作的 5G 機 - V50 ThinQ 5G。<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n從曝光資料來看，V50 ThinQ 5G 將採高屏佔比的 OLED 瀏海屏，內置 Qualcomm 最新 Snapdrago 855 + 5G X50 Modem 以及 4000mAh 電量，此外也會繼承 V40 的「前二後三」五鏡頭配置。<br />\n<br />\n不能作為首批 5G 機，V50 ThinQ 5G 的售價當然不便宜，有資料指售價會落在 130 萬 - 150 萬韓元之間，<span style=\"color: red;\">換算港幣 $9059 - $10453 左右。</span><br />\n<br />\n而尷尬的是，如果 LG 同場發表 G8 及 V50 的話，相信會大大壓縮 G8 的生存空間。"},{"pid":"a90d8fbb11e8c6f41067f76d940e227f2add34d1","tid":1024313,"uid":98223,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-16T12:43:32.000Z","msg":"唔要命<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f982582442691d4a33342c0dda0545b81d9488cb","tid":1024313,"uid":97080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-16T12:46:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c18a9b7b76ebdf2bff6b816a7bcedb74264d8df9","tid":1024313,"uid":164092,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-16T12:46:55.000Z","msg":"聽歌正<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88832405c1e4ec909adf